    "body": "ok, I think I was able to bootstrap the checkpoint sync with 3.1.0 (the hardcoded timeout was introduced in 3.1.2):\r\n\r\n```\r\nNov 08 06:59:03.462 INFO Starting checkpoint sync                remote_url: https://mainnet.checkpoint.sigp.io/, service: beacon\r\nNov 08 07:00:48.309 INFO Loaded checkpoint block and state       state_root: 0x166f7be319fadd157a506f162a5a3b06822ed792c18b5a89a2a51bac41735471, block_root: 0x86943f5962c72e56c3868fd46de62de42e1d76fec6f0b9f2bf6041e3e0bb74f6, slot: 5088800, service: beacon\r\n```\r\n\r\nit took almost 2 min from logs, from my local machine (locate in South America) to sigp public endpoint.\r\n",
